{"tid":1439990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實而家最好就係weconnect埋大陸人自由行","createTime":"2019-08-10T09:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T12:31:41.000Z","uid":5822,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5a6edd25d3efa88d611a04bff30a1150e4d5f0","tid":1439990,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:47:13.000Z","msg":"大家都知 其實我地討厭既並唔係講普通話既人<br />\n而家人格差又無禮貌既人 只係佢地咁岩講普通話<br />\n<br />\n點解憎佢地？ 因為我地係有教育水平 知道禮儀禮貌<br />\n其實好多大陸人都唔係想像中咁蠢 cctvb都訪問過大陸人點睇示威 佢地都會話尊重自由 <br />\n<br />\n而家connect大陸人就可以將信息傳達出去 再洗我地&rdquo;暴民&rdquo;底 <br />\n唔應該比政府主導晒 佢地永遠得把口 但行動力係係市民身上 <br />\n<br />\n大陸人既圈子好大 佢地會以一傳百 只要表現到同佢地報導不相乎就會質疑自己接收緊既資訊.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6f592e26f4ec5734219ab5dbdd40efd1d83c0f","tid":1439990,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"577e236278411c29286e5d812b5f7b536d856191","tid":1439990,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:53:13.000Z","msg":"【戰略】撳美金現金係最低成本嘅革命手段，成功嘅話無需攬炒，得中共自炒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439205\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439205</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fcb50b3ad202ad4748c907348129495001e96fa9","tid":1439990,"uid":92188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:53:48.000Z","msg":"其實大陸人都知佢哋接收嘅資訊好唔完全<br />\n不過冇人敢出聲咁解"},{"pid":"66042f4a1a889e7d19989b89c230a930a4b9fd77","tid":1439990,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:54:10.000Z","msg":"不好意思，借一借位：<br />\n<br />\n求求大家，盡快去換美元現鈔！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429581</a>"},{"pid":"c353965ab8fef877a4ac8d5929e9b86927197fe3","tid":1439990,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:54:56